      "TimeStopAChronosRegularBoss": {
        "id": "TimeStopAChronosRegularBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Time Freeze",
          "description": "Activates Time Freeze For 100TU. While Time Freeze is active, the user:\n- Cannot be defeated by Poison or Burn damage (including Lethal Poison).\n- Is immune to Poison, and Burn status effects.\n- Has their Active Skill TU Costs reduced by 50%. This does not stack with Quicken effects.\n- Disables the Active Skills of all other units on the battlefield (including new units that enter from reinforcements).\n\nWhen Time Freeze expires, all allies will be healed for 10% of max HP and be Purified (any negative status effects like sleep, burn or poison are removed), and all non-boss enemies on the battlefield that are below 10% of their max HP will be immediately defeated (the user is considered to have defeated those enemies with an attack) . This effect ignores Revenge passive skills, Revival passive skills, and any passive skills or effects of active skills that would prevent the enemy from being defeated.\n\nUsable once per battle. The effects of Time Freeze cannot be Purified and will be cancelled if the user is defeated. When a unit's Active Skills are disabled and they get the turn, they will lose the turn as if they were sleeping.",
          "selected": "Other units Active Skills are Disabled"
        },
